      <description>&lt;p&gt;I had fun with my little Pokémons this Advent season :-) Thanks to my love, Kasul, for all the brightness he brings to my life and every day.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/415a041c2622b2b5-scaled.jpeg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/415a041c2622b2b5-768x1024.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Welcome to Advent! Day 1 of my Pokémon Advent calendar is Applin, the Apple Pokémon.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/15e83081a5ce22c9-scaled.jpeg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/15e83081a5ce22c9-768x1024.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;I got a rocking chair for the second day of the Pokémon Advent calendar. Applin is rocking happily away.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/73d9cdd6c806ddd2-scaled.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/73d9cdd6c806ddd2-768x1024.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Rockruff, the Gen VII puppy Pokémon, joins Applin in today’s #Advent #Pokemon calendar.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
